&lt;p>Darkness in the whole existence is natural. &lt;br>
It need not be created. &lt;br>
Darkness is universal. &lt;br>
But by effort if you can bring light &lt;br>
then darkness disappears!&lt;/p>
&lt;p>Where does it go? &lt;br>
Does it get contracted or Displaced? &lt;br>
If you light all the places then &lt;br>
will there be lessor darkness &lt;br>
in the world because it has been displaced?&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>